                <rect>{{79.200000000000003, 288.39800000000002}, {86.939999761581433, 8.3249999999999886}}</rect>
            </rects>
        </annotation>
        <annotation>
            <text>Immobilization of SHRs on DNA and other nuclear structures has been studied with photobleaching techniques like Fluorescence Recovery After Photobleaching (FRAP).</text>
